Break the Language Barrier and Enjoy a Seamless Online Meeting Experience
text:
Imagine that you are attending an international meeting from your office or home, and your screen displays a live video of people from all over the world communicating with each other. However, there is one problem: you do not speak English or any of the other languages spoken by the attendees. What do you do?

No need to worry! There is now a new online meeting solution - Cross-Language Simultaneous Interpretation Online Meeting. This platform can help you break the language barrier and communicate with people from around the world in real-time!

Unlike other online meeting platforms, Cross-Language Simultaneous Interpretation Online Meeting does not require registration or downloading. You only need to open a link to join the meeting immediately. You can participate in the meeting anytime, anywhere, whether you are using a mobile phone, tablet, or computer, and enjoy high-quality simultaneous interpretation services.

In addition, the platform has an easy-to-use application that allows you to join the meeting at any time and any place, no matter where you are. You can choose to participate anonymously to ensure that your privacy is maximally protected.

We are currently looking for suitable partners to promote this platform with us. Whether you are a company, an independent marketer, or anyone interested, we welcome you to join our team. Let's work together to bring a breakthrough online meeting experience to more people! Follow me on Twitter @wngyunb2

Show HN: Transmart – Automate your i18n localization with AI
text:
Are you tired of manually translating strings in your project's i18n files? Check out Transmart! This open-source developer tool uses ChatGPT to automate i18n translation. Simply specify the base language and all the languages that need to be output, and Transmart will generate the necessary locale files for you. Transmart supports large file sizes, also support all languages that can be displayed using Intl.DisplayNames and processed by ChatGPT Additionally, it offers the ability to override AI translated values, and is compatible with i18next and chrome extension i18n

While still under active development, Transmart welcomes PRs and bug reports. Have an try:

https://github.com/Quilljou/transmart

Transcribe Audio in Browser Without API Key – WhisperAPI Hack
text:
I have successfully broken through the limitations of WhisperAPI, allowing users to send audio data captured by their microphone directly from their browser to WhisperAPI for transcription. Users can now experience ChatGPT's powerful transcription capabilities for free without having to submit an API Key. This breakthrough can be used for online meetings, transcribing conference speeches into subtitles for notes or sharing with hearing-impaired individuals, and for commercial use.

Furthermore, I have also resolved security issues such as API Key leakage, making the use of WhisperAPI more secure and reliable.

I hope that more people can support me in improving this project. I plan to open source the frontend and backend code later. Let's work together to promote this project and provide users with a better experience!
